Package: blockr.catbreeds
Title: A Custom blockr Data Block for The Cat API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Granjon", email = "david.granjon@cynkra.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A small example extension for the useR! 2026 blockr talk. Ships a
    bundled cat breeds dataset (sourced from The Cat API) as a set of blockr
    blocks, registered with the block registry on load. The dataset is rebuilt
    from the API on demand via the data-raw pipeline, so the package never
    queries the API at runtime.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
